snippet.title: Life is Feudal: Forest Village
snippet.description:
We are proud to introduce you to the first title of the Life is Feudal franchise, which is being developed by a team of fellow indie developers who call themselves Mindillusion!
It is a new upcoming city builder with survival aspects in a harsh environment. Vote for us on a Greenlight: http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=709170194
